{
  "stem": "5516.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember the-- the name and the address and the street, I remember.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And nobody could write letters, just the American soldiers-- he said, I will send it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Write a letter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I will send a letter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He sent a letter to-- it's a cousin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My-- my uncle my father's brother, he died but he had sons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The one son answered.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] He answered.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He say, how can you prove you're a cousin?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I had a little bit idea, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The picture I'll show you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remembered my father sent them a picture from the family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I told him, if you've got this picture, you will see I'm on this picture holding hands like this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After they see, he answered me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he say, I saw the picture.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We got the picture, and you are there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They sent me out an affidavit to come to United States.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I registered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, if I would be smart enough, and I didn't know nothing, I would register I'm born in Germany, I would go in two weeks.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I registered I am born in Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Lithuania got four people a year to come in and 275,000 registered.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I cannot come [LAUGHS] in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So after this, Truman made a law.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then after a [? quarter ?] for these people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I come over through United Nations.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I'm thinking, people who come in through the United Nations they didn't give a name from a relative, they gave them a hotel and a job.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I gave a name, so they put me on a train like in Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they sent me over to this bus.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I come over and I didn't have luck with my cousin.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
